    "extractedFrom": "territory[id=CA].fixedLine.nationalNumberPattern",
    "notes": "Added alongside us.json to prove calling code 1 (NANP) can resolve to more than one region: US and Canada share calling code 1 but have disjoint area-code allocations, so parse() tries each region sharing a matched calling code and returns whichever one's pattern actually validates the number. Same localOnly-length-dropped rationale as us.json."
  },
